## Database Conventions
- UUID primary keys (@default(uuid()))
- DateTime fields with @default(now()) and @updatedAt
- snake_case mapping: @@map("table_name") and @map("column_name")
- Cascade deletes for parent-child: onDelete: Cascade
- JSON fields for flexible config (typed with Zod at runtime)
- Encrypted fields use lib/crypto.ts encrypt/decrypt

## Component Conventions
- Use shadcn/ui primitives: Button, Card, Input, Dialog, Sheet, Table, Badge, etc.
- Tailwind classes only — no inline styles, no CSS modules
- Form components use react-hook-form + zod resolver
- Loading states use Skeleton components
- Toast notifications via sonner (already configured)
- Data tables follow the pattern in patients/page.tsx

## API Route Conventions
- GET for list/detail, POST for create, PATCH for update, DELETE for remove
- Validate request body with zod schemas
- Return NextResponse.json() with appropriate status codes
- Auth check: import { auth } from "@/auth" and validate session
- Error responses: { error: string } with 400/401/403/404/500
- Audit log writes for HIPAA-sensitive operations

